Quiz Time Overview
This project is a basic quiz application built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The application presents a set of multiple-choice questions to the user, provides feedback on their answers, and allows them to retake the quiz.

Project Structure
basic-js-quiz/
-index.html
-style.css
-script.js

To run this project, you need a web browser and a code editor (optional) for editing the files.

Usage
Open the Quiz:
Open the index.html file in a web browser to start the quiz.

Answer the Questions:
Select an answer for each question.

Submit Answers:
Click the "Submit Answers" button to see your results.

View Results:
The quiz will display your score and highlight correct and incorrect answers.

Retake Quiz:
Click the "Retake Quiz" button to reset the quiz and try again.

